Hi,
As discussed in the newsgroup (see below). It would be nice to have a possibility to control the xmlhelper deresolve behavior.
A nice-to-have optional behavior would be that the xml resource (xmlhelper?) and EObjectResolver would be able to gracefully handle non-existing references (for example replacing the non-existing reference with a null value, or do not add to a list). 

